		Dear {!Product__c.First_Name__c},<br>
		
		<h2 style="text-align: center;"><b><u> Overdue Account</b></u></h2>
		<br>
Our records indicate that your account with Affirm Financial is past due and you have now missed 2  
                             minimum payments. 		
		<br><br>
		We have made several attempts to get in touch with you but have not been successful. We ask that you 
                remit payment immediately or contact us to make payment arrangements if necessary.
		Failure to make payment may further negatively impact your credit rating with the possibility of being denied future credit. 
<br><br>
  
The amount required to bring your account into good standing is  <strong> {!Product__c.Product_Payment_Amount__c}. </strong>
		<br/><br/>
		<strong>
		Choose one of our convenient payment options listed below:
		</strong>
